@startuml
title 音频AI推荐时序图

actor 用户 as User
participant ":上传页面" as Frontend
participant ":RecommendController" as RC
participant ":RecommendService" as RS
participant ":RecommendRecordDao" as RRD
participant ":DB" as DB

User -> Frontend: 1:选择音频，点击上传
Frontend -> RC: 2:上传请求
RC -> RS: 3:校验文件，保存上传记录
RS -> RRD: 4:插入上传记录
RRD -> DB: 5:写入上传记录表
DB --> Frontend: 6:上传成功
Frontend --> User: 7:等待分析

User -> Frontend: 8:点击开始分析推荐
Frontend -> RC: 9:分析请求
RC -> RS: 10:调用音频特征提取和AI语义增强
RS -> RS: 11:遍历曲库计算相似度
RS -> RS: 12:筛选排序取Top20
RS -> RRD: 13:写入推荐记录
RRD -> DB: 14:写入推荐表
DB --> Frontend: 15:分析完成
Frontend --> User: 16:展示推荐歌曲列表

@enduml
